quran[5{c,v,t}:
10,21,"logon ka haal yeh hai ke museebat ke baad jab hum un ko rehmat ka maza chakkhatay hain to foran hi woh hamari nshanyon ke maamla mein chaal bazyan shuru kar dete hain un se kaho “Allah apni chaal mein tum se ziyada taiz hai, is ke farishtay tumhari sab mkaryoN ko qalam band kar rahay hain """
10,22,"woh Allah hi hai jo tum ko khushki aur tri mein chalata hai chunancha jab tum kashtiyon mein sawaar ho kar baad-e mawafiq par Ferhan o Shadan safar kar rahay hotay ho aur phir yakayak baad-e mukhalif ka zor hota hai aur har taraf se moajoon ke thpirhe lagtay hain aur musafir samajh letay hain ke tufaan mein ghar gay, uss waqt sab apne deen ko Allah hi ke liye khalis kar ke is se Duayen mangte hain ke “ agar to ne hum ko is bulaa se nijaat day di to hum shukar guzaar bande banin ge """
10,23,"magar jab woh un ko bacha laita hai to phir wohi log haq se munharif ho kar zameen mein baghaawat karne lagtay hain logo, tumhari yeh baghaawat Ulti tumahray hi khilaaf par rahi hai duniya ke chand roza mazay hain ( lُot lau ), phir hamari taraf tumhe palat kar aana hai, uss waqt hum tumhe bta den ge ke tum kya kuch karte rahay ho"
10,24,"duniya ki yeh zindagi ( jis ke nashay mein mast ho kar tum hamari nshanyon se ghaflat bart rahay ho ) is ki misaal aisi hai jaisay aasman se hum ne pani barsaya to zameen ki pedawar, jisay aadmi aur janwar sab khatay hain, khoob ghani ho gayi, phir ain uss waqt jabkay zameen apni bahhar par thi aur khityan bani snori khari theen aur un ke maalik yeh samajh rahay thay ke ab hum un se faida aُthane par Qadir hain, yakayak raat ko ya din ko hamara hukum aa gaya aur hum ne usay aisa ghaarat kar ke rakh diya ke goya kal wahan kuch tha hi nahi is terhan hum nishanain khol khol kar paish karte hain unn logon ke liye jo sochnay samajhney walay hain"
10,25,( tum iss na paidaar zindagi ke fraib mein mubtala ho rahay ho ) aur Allah tumhe daar salam ki taraf dawat day raha hai ( hadaayat uss ke ikhtiyar mein hai ) jis ko woh chahta hai seedha rasta dikha deta hai
